# ================================================
# CODEOWNERS MAINTENANCE
# ================================================

# This file should be updated when:
# - New team members join with specific expertise
# - New packages or major components are added
# - Security requirements change
# - Documentation structure is modified

# To modify this file:
# 1. Update the owner assignments
# 2. Ensure the changes are reviewed by existing owners
# 3. Test that the new assignments work correctly
# 4. Update documentation if needed

